        <section id="features">
            <h2>3. Platform Feature Matrix</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>**Monetization Suite:** Tools for creators to establish pricing, manage promotions, and generate custom discount coupons.</li>
                <li>**Performance Dashboards:** Comprehensive user interfaces providing metrics on content performance (views, downloads, revenue) and personalized transaction history.</li>
                <li>**Administrative Interface:** Centralized control panel for platform operators to manage user access, conduct content moderation, and generate usage/payment reports.</li>
                <li>**Notification Service:** Automated system alerts for new content additions, critical platform announcements, and personalized transaction status updates.</li>
                <li>**Content Integrity:** System designation for **Verified** content, indicating resources sourced from authenticated or peer-reviewed providers.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

