        <section id="faqs">
            <h2>4. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
            <dl>
                <dt><strong>Q:</strong> What is the policy regarding content ownership?</dt>
                <dd><strong>A:</strong> Content creators retain full intellectual property rights to their submitted original material, subject to the Vidyari **Terms of Service**.</dd>
                
                <dt><strong>Q:</strong> What are the prerequisites for successful file upload?</dt>
                <dd><strong>A:</strong> Files must be an explicitly **Supported File Type** and adhere to the maximum **7GB** size constraint. Uploads must not violate copyright or platform integrity policies.</dd>
                
                <dt><strong>Q:</strong> How do I apply a coupon code?</dt>
                <dd><strong>A:</strong> Coupon codes are entered and validated on the final **Checkout/Payment** page prior to initiating the transaction.</dd>
                
                <dt><strong>Q:</strong> What is the procedure for a failed payment transaction?</dt>
                <dd><strong>A:</strong> Users must verify the status in the Dashboard transaction history. If the asset remains unavailable, contact Support immediately, providing the specific **Transaction ID** for manual resolution or refund processing.</dd>
            </dl>
        </section>

