        <section id="ai-assistance">
            <h2>5. AI Assistance and Integration</h2>
            <p>The platform utilizes an integrated **AI Assistant** system designed to streamline content discovery, user support, and operational guidance.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>**AI Functionality:**
                    <ul>
                        <li>**Semantic Search:** Facilitates complex natural language queries for content retrieval based on context and metadata.</li>
                        <li>**Operational Guidance:** Provides automated, step-by-step instructions for standard user tasks (e.g., uploading, dashboard navigation).</li>
                        <li>**Diagnostic Support:** Offers preliminary troubleshooting for common system faults (e.g., login failure, size constraint errors).</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="note">
                **Security Constraint:** The AI Assistant operates exclusively on public and documented platform data. It **does not** possess access to private account credentials, payment instruments, or sensitive user information. For private issues, use the dedicated **Support** channel.
            </div>
        </section>

