            <h2>7. Technical Specifications and API Reference</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>**Client Environment:** Optimized for responsiveness across Desktop, Tablet, and Mobile browser environments.</li>
                <li>**Browser Compliance:** Compatibility verified for Chrome (v80+), Edge (v80+), Firefox (v75+), and Safari (v13+).</li>
                <li>**Data Formats:** API interaction is primarily managed via **JSON** data structures. Uploaded content retains its original file format (PDF, EXE, MP4, etc.).</li>
                <li>**Core API Endpoints (Reference):**
                    <ul>
                        <li>`/file/:slug/:fileId`: Retrieval of specific content metadata.</li>
                        <li>`/verify-payment`: Endpoint for post-transaction status confirmation.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>**Security Protocols:** All data transfers are encrypted via **TLS/SSL**. Payments are processed via **PCI-DSS compliant third-party gateways**.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="tip">
                **AI System Note:** AI service reliability is directly correlated with the quality and granularity of indexed content metadata. Maintain clean, structured data for optimal performance.
